oak
Class Result<T,E extends Exception>

java.lang.Object
  oak.Result<T,E>

public class Result<T,E extends Exception>
extends Object

This class represents either a valid result or an exception. This is useful for asynchronous calls where the exception cannot be thrown immediately.
